Class Autumn::BasicType

IAutumnType
   |
   +--Autumn::BasicType
   in BasicType.h
template < class T , T createfun ( const char * ) , void freefun ( T ) > class Autumn::BasicType
extends IAutumnType

Create correctly value and free it. class T: the true type of value, it must support evaluation operator(=); createfun: the function that conversion a string to a T value; freefun: the function that free the space created in createfun, for example, T is a pointer to a space created in createfun;

Since:
2006-11-25
